The view template "body missing" cascade is a [[cascade|Cascades]] used by the default view template to choose the template for displaying the ''missing tiddler'' hint.

The default missing tiddler hint template cascade consists of:

#  If the tiddler is a missing tiddler then use the template $:/config/ViewTemplateBodyMissingFilters/missing/hint to show the "missing tiddler hint".

You can see the current settings for the missing tiddler cascade in $:/ControlPanel under the ''Info'' -> ''Advanced'' -> ''Cascades''  -> ''View Template Body Missing'' tab.

